<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>台南小吃</title>
    {{! 載入font awesome }}
    <script
      src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/c7704bf3c1.js"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    {{! 載入bootstrap }}
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/bootstrap.css" />
    {{! 載入Google fonts }}
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+TC&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    {{! 載入CSS }}
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/stylesheets/style.css" />
    {{! 載入favicon }}
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/favicon.ico" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <nav class="navbar navbar-light bg-light">
        <div class="container-fluid">
          <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
            <img
              src="/images/undraw_cooking_p7m1.svg"
              alt=""
              width="30"
              height="24"
              class="d-inline-block align-text-top"
            />
            <span>2023台南精選小吃</span>
          </a>
          <button
            class="navbar-toggler"
            type="button"
            data-bs-toggle="collapse"
            data-bs-target="#navbarNav"
            aria-controls="navbarNav"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-label="Toggle navigation"
          >
            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
          </button>
          <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
            <ul class="navbar-nav">
              <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link" aria-current="page" href="/">Home</a>
              </li>
              <li class="nav-item">
                <a
                  class="nav-link"
                  href="#"
                  data-bs-toggle="modal"
                  data-bs-target="#exampleModal"
                >About</a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </nav>

      <!-- Modal -->
      <div
        class="modal fade"
        id="exampleModal"
        tabindex="-1"
        aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel"
        aria-hidden="true"
      >
        <div class="modal-dialog">
          <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
              <h5 class="modal-title" id="exampleModalLabel">關於此專案</h5>
              <button
                type="button"
                class="btn-close"
                data-bs-dismiss="modal"
                aria-label="Close"
              ></button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
              <p
              >使用node.js的web應用框架Express.js設定動態路由，搭配樣板引擎handlebars讀取json檔案，並製作搜尋功能可搜尋台南精選的特色小吃。</p>
              <p><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i> 使用技術：</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Express.js</li>
                <li>HTML/CSS/JavaScript</li>
                <li>SCSS</li>
                <li>RWD</li>
              </ul>
              <p><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i> 使用套件：</p>
              <ul>
                <li>handlebars</li>
                <li>bootstrap</li>
                <li>Google Fonts</li>
                <li>Font Awesome</li>
              </ul>
              <p><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i> 設計功能：</p>
              <ul>
                <li>使用者可以在搜尋欄輸入<strong
                  >關鍵字</strong>（小吃名稱或食物分類）以進行搜尋</li>
                <li
                >使用者可點擊首頁內的任一小吃圖片，即可瀏覽此小吃的詳細資訊</li>
                <li>使用者可點擊導覽列的icon或標題名稱回到首頁</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
              <button
                type="button"
                class="btn btn-secondary"
                data-bs-dismiss="modal"
              >Close</button>

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="banner"></div>
    </header>
    <main>
      <!-- partial templates will replace the part of "body" here -->
      {{{body}}}

      <div class="alert alert-warning" role="alert">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-exclamation"></i>
        特別註明：此專案內的圖片文案皆取自<a
          href="https://www.elle.com/tw/life/foodie/g10133/tainan-food-list/"
        >台南必吃美食大統整！牛肉湯、蝦仁飯、冰品⋯不敗小吃完整清單一次收！</a></div>
    </main>

    <footer>
      Copyright © 2023 AshleyChou. All rights reserved.
    </footer>

    {{! 載入bootstrap }}
    <script src="/javascripts/popper.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/bootstrap.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>